description: On obvious spoof of Marvel's Dead Pool (who is already a spoof of DC's Deathstroke), Red Tool kidnaps Harley Quinn at a roller derby match by using knock out gas. He takes her to the top of a ferris wheel and tried to show her and animated video of his "origin story" he made but forgot to charge his phone so instead tells her. She eventually escapes but discovers when she gets home that he has tattooed a phone number and a red hammer on her bottom. The phone number is a voice message telling her to meet him at a church, where he has kidnapped some witnesses and the priest to perform a marriage ceremony.
